text: Ah that’s so cool!! Sounds nice to go to traditional art :hugging_face: yeah it’s going okay, been taking a break for a bit, felt a bit burned out :joy: but I’m meaning to sort out my application for the framestore internship before the end of the month
I know that they want photorealism so I’m stuck for ideas on what to make, not sure whether to stay away from cars and things like that since everyone makes them
